CHECK:COMPARISON_TO_NULL: Comparison to NULL could be written "!vaddr"
#134: FILE: drivers/gpu/drm/i915/i915_gem.c:232:
+	if (vaddr == NULL)

Comparisons to NULL in the form (foo == NULL) or (foo != NULL)
are better written as (!foo) and (foo).

